com.interpss.core.algo

Interface AclfDclfAlgorithm<TDcAlgo extends DclfAlgorithm>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    com.hazelcast.nio.serialization.DataSerializable, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, IAclfNetBVisitor, LoadflowAlgorithm, NameTag, NetworkRef<BaseAclfNetwork<?,?>>, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AclfDclfAlgorithmImpl

    public interface AclfDclfAlgorithm<TDcAlgo extends DclfAlgorithm>
extends LoadflowAlgorithm
    A representation of the model object 'Aclf Dclf Algorithm'. Loadflow algorithm with a Dclf algorithm referencing the same AclfNetwork object. The AclfNet object is read-only when performing Dclf calculation.

    The following features are supported:

    • Dclf Algo
    See Also:
